content: {'id': '7886d300-4dfc-37a7-8849-6ca8cc84f5ea', 'contentType': 'STORY', 'title': "India's Bajaj Auto flags lower-than-planned EV output on rare earths crunch", 'description': '', 'summary': '(Reuters) -Bajaj Auto will not meet its electric vehicles delivery target in the second-quarter as the Indian automaker grapples with a shortage of rare earth magnets, a senior executive said on Wednesday.
